Top-level folders in Coin are cli, archive, docker, and nebula; I’ll now list each one’s immediate subfolders for a full two-level view.

<TASKS>
{
  "tasks": [
    {
      "type": "run_command",
      "cwd": ".",
      "command": "[ -d Coin ] && for d in Coin/*/; do bn=$(basename \"$d\"); echo \"$bn/\"; ls -1p \"$d\" | grep '/$' | sed 's:/$::' | sed 's/^/  - /'; echo; done || echo '__COIN_DIR_NOT_FOUND__'"
    }
  ]
}
</TASKS>
